  <source>Taiho Pharmaceutical Co., Ltd.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This controlled study is designed to evaluate the efficacy of TS-1 on survival compared with
      surgery alone. Patients will be randomly assigned to receive either surgery alone or surgery
      followed by treatment with TS-1 within 45 days after curative resection (curability A or B).
      To assess the efficacy, data on recurrence and survival will be collected from the time of
      enrollment until 5 years after surgery. To evaluate safety, data on adverse events will be
      collected from the time of enrollment until 1 year after surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
